#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The wallet subsystem provides a convenient and secure way to manage all your "
"passwords."
msgstr ""
"Turvalaegaste alamsüsteem pakub mugava ja turvalise võimaluse hallata oma "
"paroole."

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"
msgstr "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kwallet"
msgstr "Kwallet"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "passwords"
msgstr "paroolid"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "forms"
msgstr "vormid"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Sissejuhatus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Computer users have a very large amount of data to manage, some of which is "
"sensitive. In particular, you will typically have many passwords to manage. "
"Remembering them is difficult and writing them down on paper or in a text "
"file is insecure."
msgstr ""
"Arvutikasutajatel on enamasti väga palju erilaadseid andmeid, osa neist üsna "
"tundlikud. Näiteks on väga paljudes kohtades vaja anda parool. Nende "
"meelespidamine pole alati mitte lihtne ning kirjapanemine paberile või "
"tekstifaili kujutab endast ohtu turvalisusele."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwallet5; provides a secure way to store passwords and other secret "
"information, allowing the user to remember only a single password instead of "
"numerous different passwords and credentials."
msgstr ""
"&kwallet5; pakub turvalist võimalust salvestada paroole ja muud salajast "
"teavet, lastes kasutajal paljude paroolide ja muude tunnuste asemel meelde "
"jätta ainult ühe parooli."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a Wallet"
msgstr "Turvalaeka loomine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Wallet is a password storage. It is usually sufficient to have just one "
"wallet secured by one master password but you can organize your large "
"collection of passwords by wallets using &kwalletmanager5;."
msgstr ""
"Laegas kujutab endast paroolide hoidlat. Tavaliselt piisab ühestainsast "
"laekast, mida kaitseb ülemparool, kuid soovi korral saab oma rohked paroolid "
"jagada ka eri laegaste vahel, mida aitab teha turvalaeka haldur."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default a wallet named <guilabel>kdewallet</guilabel> will be used to "
"store your passwords. This wallet is secured by your login password and will "
"automatically be opened at login, if kwallet_pam is installed and properly "
"configured. On certain distros (&eg; Archlinux) kwallet_pam is not installed "
"by default"
msgstr ""
"Vaikimisi kasutatakse sinu paroolide salvestamiseks turvalaegast nimega "
"<guilabel>kdewallet</guilabel>. Seda turvab sinu sisselogimise parool ja see "
"avatakse sisselogimisel automaatselt, kui kwallet_pam on paigaldatud ja "
"sobivalt seadistatud. Mõningates distributsioonidees (&eg; ArchLinuxis) ei "
"ole kwallet_pam vaikimisi paigaldatud."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other wallets have to be opened manually."
msgstr "Teised turvalaekad tuleb käsitsi avada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are two ways to create a new wallet:"
msgstr "Uut turvalaegast saab luua kahel moel:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the menu item <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>New "
"Wallet</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the &kwalletmanager5;"
msgstr ""
"Menüükäsuga <menuchoice><guimenu>Fail</guimenu><guimenuitem>Uus turvalaegas</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> turvalaeka halduris"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guibutton>New</guibutton> button in the &systemsettings; module "
"<guilabel>KDE Wallet</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"Nupuga <guibutton>Uus</guibutton> Süsteemi seadistuste moodulis "
"<guilabel>KDE turvalaegas</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have not created a wallet yet, see section <link linkend=\"kwallet-"
"using\">Using &kwallet5;</link>."
msgstr ""
"Kui sa ei ole veel laegast loonud, vaata osa <link linkend=\"kwallet-using"
"\">&kwallett;i kasutamine</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kwallet5; offers two different ways to store your data:"
msgstr "&kwallet5; pakub kaht viisi sinu andmeid salvestada:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Select encryption</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Krüptimise valimine</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Select encryption</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Krüptimise valimine</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "Blowfish encryption"
msgstr "Blowfishi krüptimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwallet5; saves this sensitive data for you in a strongly encrypted file, "
"accessible by all applications, and protected with a master password that "
"you define."
msgstr ""
"&kwallet5; salvestab sellised tundlikud andmed tugeva krüpteeringuga faili, "
"millele pääsevad ligi kõik rakendused ja mis on kaitstud peaparooliga."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Create a blowfish encrypted wallet</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Blowfishi krüpteeringuga turvalaeka loomine</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Create a blowfish encrypted wallet</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Blowfishi krüpteeringuga turvalaeka loomine</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The data is encrypted with the <ulink url=\"http://www.schneier.com/blowfish."
"html\">Blowfish symmetric block cipher algorithm</ulink>, the algorithm key "
"is derived from the <ulink url=\"http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc3174.txt\">SHA-1 "
"hash</ulink> of the password, with a key length of 156 bits (20 bytes). The "
"data into the wallet file is also hashed with SHA-1 and checked before the "
"data is deciphered and accessible by the applications."
msgstr ""
"Andmed krüptitakse <ulink url=\"http://www.schneier.com/blowfish.html"
"\">Blowfishi sümmeetrilise plokkšifri algoritmiga</ulink>, algoritmi võti on "
"tuletatud parooli <ulink url=\"http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc3174.txt\">SHA-1 "
"räsist</ulink> ning võtme pikkus on 156 bitti (20 baiti). Laekafaili andmed "
"räsitakse samuti SHA-1 abil ning neid kontrollitakse, enne kui andmed "
"dešifreeritakse ja tehakse rakendustele kättesaadavaks."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "GPG encryption"
msgstr "GPG krüptimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"GnuPG offers some very strong encryption algorithms and uses passphrase "
"protected long keys."
msgstr ""
"GnuPG pakub mõningaid väga tugevaid krüptoalgoritme ning kasutab "
"paroolifraasiga kaitstud pikki võtmeid."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>No GPG key found</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>PGP võtit ei leitud</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>No GPG key found</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>PGP võtit ei leitud</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The screenshots above show the case where an encryption capable GPG key was "
"not found on the system. Please use applications like &kgpg; or &kleopatra; "
"to create a key and try again."
msgstr ""
"Ülalolevat pilti näeb juhul, kui süsteemis ei leitud krüptimiseks sobilikku "
"GPG võtit. Palun kasuta võtme loomiseks mõnda rakendust, näiteks &kgpg; või "
"&kleopatra;, ja proovi uuesti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a GPG key was found you will get the next dialog where you can select a "
"key to use for your new wallet."
msgstr ""
"Kui GPG võti leitakse, näed järgmist dialoogi, kus saad valida uue "
"turvalaeka jaoks kasutatava võtme."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Select an encryption key</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Krüptovõtme valimine</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Select an encryption key</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Krüptovõtme valimine</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwallet5; will now use GPG when storing wallets and when opening them. The "
"passphrase dialog only shows once. Even if the wallet is closed after "
"initial open, subsequent opening will occur silently during the same session."
msgstr ""
"&kwallet5; hakkab nüüd turvalaegastesse salvestamisel ja nende avamisel "
"kasutama GPG võtit. Paroolifraasi dialoogi näeb ainult ühe korra. Isegi kui "
"turvalaegas suletakse pärast esimest avamist, toimuvad järgmised avamised "
"sama seansi ajal vaikselt, kasutajat täiendavalt häirimata."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The same session can handle simultaneously both file formats. &kwallet5; "
"will transparently detect the file format and load the correct backend to "
"handle it."
msgstr ""
"Ühe seansi ajal võivad korraga kasutusel olla mõlemad failivormingud. "
"&kwallet5; tuvastab läbipaistvalt failivormingu ja laadib just vajaliku "
"taustaprogrammi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To use your sensitive data from your classic wallet with the new backend "
"follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Oma klassikalises turvalaekas leiduvate tundlike andmete kasutamiseks uue "
"taustaprogrammiga tuleb järgida järgmisi samme:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a new GPG based wallet"
msgstr "Loo uus GPG-põhine turvalaegas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Launch &kwalletmanager5; using &krunner; (<keycombo>&Alt; <keycap>F2</"
"keycap></keycombo>) or other application launcher (menu) and select your old "
"wallet. Then choose <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Export "
"as encrypted</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to create an archive file with your "
"sensitive data."
msgstr ""
"Käivita turvalaeka haldur, kasutades &krunner;it (<keycombo>&Alt; "
"<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo>) või mõnda muud rakenduste käivitajat "
"(menüüd) ja vali oma vana turvalaegas; seejärel vali menüükäsk "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Fail</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ekspordi krüptitult</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, millega lood oma tundlikke andmeid sisaldava "
"arhiivifaili."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the new GPG based wallet then choose <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Import encrypted</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and select "
"the file you just saved."
msgstr ""
"Vali uus GPG-põhine turvalaegas ja seejärel menüükäsk "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Fail</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Impordi krüptitult</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ning vali äsja salvestatud fail."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to &systemsettings; <menuchoice><guimenu>Account Details</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>KDE Wallet</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and select the newly "
"created GPG based wallet from the <guilabel>Select wallet to use as default</"
"guilabel> combobox."
msgstr ""
"Vali Süsteemi seadistustes <menuchoice><guimenu>Konto üksikasjad</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>KDE turvalaegas</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ning vali "
"liitkastist <guilabel>Vaikimisi kasutatav turvalaegas</guilabel> GPG-põhine "
"turvalaegas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively use <guimenuitem>Import a wallet</guimenuitem> but in that "
"case you have to select the <filename class=\"extension\">.kwl</filename> "
"file corresponding to your old wallet, located in the folder <filename class="
"\"directory\">kwalletd</filename> in <userinput>qtpaths --paths "
"GenericDataLocation</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Fail</guimenu><guimenuitem>Impordi turvalaegas</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, aga sel juhul tuleb valida <filename class="
"\"extension\">.kwl</filename>-fail, mis vastab sinu vanale turvalaekale (see "
"asub kataloogis <filename class=\"directory\">kwalletd</filename> asukohas "
"<userinput>qtpaths --paths GenericDataLocation</userinput>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwallet5; supports multiple wallets, so for the most secure operation, you "
"should use one wallet for local passwords, and another for network passwords "
"and form data. You can configure this behavior in the &kwallet5; "
"&systemsettings; module, however the default setting is to store everything "
"in one wallet named <guilabel>kdewallet</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"&kwallet5; toetab mitme turvalaeka kasutamist, nii et võimalikult suure "
"turvalisuse huvides tuleks kasutada üht turvalaegast kohalike paroolide, "
"teist aga võrguparoolide ja vormiandmete tarbeks. Sellist käitumist saab "
"seadistada Süsteemi seadistuste &kwallet5;i moodulis. Vaikimisi "
"salvestatakse siiski kõik ühte laekasse nimega <guilabel>kdewallet</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A wallet is by default closed, which means that you must supply a password "
"to open it. Once the wallet is opened, the contents can be read by any user "
"process, so this may be a security issue."
msgstr ""
"Vaikimisi on turvalaegas suletud, mis tähendab, et pead selle avamiseks "
"andma parooli. Laeka avamise järel pääseb selle sisule ligi iga kasutaja, "
"nii et siin võib peituda teatav turberisk."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kwallet5;"
msgstr "&kwallet5;i kasutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you visit &eg; the &kde; bugtracker and enter the login data for the "
"first time, a dialog pops up offering to store the password in an encrypted "
"wallet:"
msgstr ""
"Kui külastad &eg; &kde; vigade registreerimise lehekülge ning sisestad seal "
"esimest korda sisselogimisandmed, ilmub dialoog, mis pakub võimaluse "
"salvestada parooli krüptitud turvalaekasse:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Request to save login information</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Sisselogimisteabe salvestamise päring</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Request to save login information</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Sisselogimisteabe salvestamise päring</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to store this information, select <guibutton>Store</guibutton> "
"to proceed. In case you did not create a wallet so far, the next dialog asks "
"for the encryption backend and creates a wallet named kdewallet."
msgstr ""
"Kui soovid selle teabe salvestada, klõpsa jätkamiseks nupule "
"<guibutton>Salvesta</guibutton>. Kui sa ei ole seni veel turvalaegast "
"loonud, palub järgmine dialoog valida krüptimise taustaprogrammi ning loob "
"laeka nimega kdewallet."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next time you visit the same website again, the application retrieves the "
"login data from an open wallet and prefills the forms with these secrets."
msgstr ""
"Kui külastad järgmine kord sama veebilehte, hangib rakendus "
"sisselogimisandmed avatud turvalaekast ja täidab vormi väljad ise "
"saladustega."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Prefilled login information</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Sisselogimisteabe automaatne sisestamine</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Prefilled login information</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Sisselogimisteabe automaatne sisestamine</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the wallet is closed the application requests to open the wallet. Enter "
"the wallet password and click the <guibutton>Open</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Kui turvalaegas on suletud, soovib rakendus seda avada. Sisesta selle parool "
"ja klõpsa nupule <guibutton>Ava</guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Request to open a wallet</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Turvalaeka avamise päring</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Request to open a wallet</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Turvalaeka avamise päring</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This connects the application to the wallet, enables it to read the login "
"data from the wallet and to restore the login information for this website. "
"Once an application is connected to the wallet, it can automatically restore "
"any login information stored in the wallet."
msgstr ""
"See loob ühenduse rakenduse ja turvalaeka vahel, võimaldab rakendusel lugeda "
"laekast sisselogimisandmed ning rakendada need antud veebileheküljel. Niipea "
"kui rakendus on laekaga ühenduse loonud, rakendatakse automaatselt kogu "
"sinna salvestatud sisselogimisteave."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kwalletmanager5;"
msgstr "Turvalaeka haldur"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwalletmanager5; serves a number of functions. Firstly it allows you to see "
"if any wallets are open, which wallets those are, and which applications are "
"using each wallet. You can disconnect an application's access to a wallet "
"from within the &kwalletmanager5;."
msgstr ""
"Turvalaeka haldur täidab mitut ülesannet. Esiteks võimaldab see näha, kas "
"mõni laegas on avatud ja kui on, siis milline, samuti seda, milline rakendus "
"millist laegast kasutab. Turvalaeka haldur võimaldab ka katkestada rakenduse "
"ligipääsu laekale."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may also manage the wallets installed on the system, creating and "
"deleting wallets and manipulating their contents (changing keys, ...)."
msgstr ""
"Selle abil saab ka süsteemi paigaldatud laekaid hallata, neid luua ja "
"kustutada ning nende sisu (näiteks võtmeid) muuta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kwalletmanager5; application is launched with <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Applications</guimenu><guisubmenu>System</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Wallet Management Tool</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the "
"application launcher. Alternatively start &krunner; with shortcut <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> and enter "
"<command>kwalletmanager5</command>."
msgstr ""
"Turvalaeka halduri saab käivitada rakenduste käivitajast "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Rakendused</guimenu><guisubmenu>Süsteem</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Turvalaeka haldur</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Teine "
"võimalus on käivitada &krunner; kiirklahviga <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> ja anda seal korraldus "
"<command>kwalletmanager5</command>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click once on the system tray wallet icon to display the &kwalletmanager5; "
"window."
msgstr "Klõps süsteemisalve ikoonil avab turvalaeka halduri akna."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Main window with one wallet</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Peaaken ühe turvalaekaga</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Main window with one wallet</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Peaaken ühe turvalaekaga</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Main window with one wallet</para>"
msgstr "<para>Peaaken ühe turvalaekaga</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Wallet Window"
msgstr "Turvalaeka aken"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have more than one wallet all available wallets are shown on the left."
msgstr "Kui sul on turvalaekaid üle ühe, on kõik need näha vasakul."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on a wallet in the &kwalletmanager5; window will display that "
"wallet's status and the contents of an opened wallet. A wallet may contain "
"any number of folders, which allow storing of password information. By "
"default a wallet will contain folders named Form Data and Passwords."
msgstr ""
"Klõps turvalaeka halduri aknas laeka ikoonil näitab antud laeka olekut ja "
"avatud laeka sisu. Laekal võib olla mitu sahtlit, kuhu saab salvestada "
"paroolidega seotud teabe. Vaikimisi on laekal sahtlid nimetustega Vormi "
"andmed ja Paroolid."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Main window with two wallets</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Peaaken kahe turvalaekaga</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Main window with two wallets</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Peaaken kahe turvalaekaga</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Main window with two wallets</para>"
msgstr "<para>Peaaken kahe turvalaekaga</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guibutton>Open</guibutton> to display the content of a closed wallet. "
"You will be requested to enter the master password."
msgstr ""
"Nupuga <guibutton>Ava</guibutton> saab lasta näidata suletud turvalaeka "
"sisu. Sinu käest soovitakse teada ülemparooli."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid "Contents tab"
msgstr "Sisu kaart"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guilabel>Contents</guilabel> tab has three sections:"
msgstr "Kaardil <guilabel>Sisu</guilabel> on kolm osa:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid "A search line to filter the items of the current wallet"
msgstr "Otsingurida aktiivse laeka elementide filtreerimiseks"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The tree view of the folders contained in the wallet. Click the <guiicon>&gt;"
"</guiicon> / <guiicon>v</guiicon> icons to expand or collapse the tree view."
msgstr ""
"Laeka sahtlite puuvaade. Puuvaate lahti- või kokkukerimiseks klõpsa "
"ikoonidele <guiicon>&gt;</guiicon> / <guiicon>v</guiicon>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The contents of the selected folder entry at the right side. By default the "
"password and value are hidden. To display and edit them enable "
"<guilabel>Show values</guilabel> or click the <guilabel>Show Contents</"
"guilabel> button."
msgstr ""
"Valitud sahtli sisu paremal. Vaikimisi on parool ja väärtus peidetud. Nende "
"nägemiseks ja muutmiseks närgi <guilabel>Väärtuste näitamine</guilabel> või "
"klõpsa nupule <guilabel>Näita sisu</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Folders may be added or deleted via the context menu, and selecting a folder "
"will update the folder entry list and the summary display. Selecting a "
"folder entry will update the entry contents pane, and allow you to edit that "
"entry."
msgstr ""
"Sahtleid saab lisada või kustutada kontekstimenüü abil, mõne sahtli valimine "
"uuendab sahtlikirjete loendit ja kokkuvõtet. Sahtlikirje valimine uuendab "
"kirje sisupaneeli ja võimaldab antud kirjet redigeerida."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Entries may also be created, renamed or deleted via the context menu for the "
"folder contents."
msgstr ""
"Ka kirjeid saab luua, kustutada või nende nime muuta sahtli sisu "
"kontekstimenüü abil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All folders and entries may be dragged and dropped into other wallets or "
"folders respectively. This allows a user to easily package up a new wallet "
"for transfer to another environment. For instance, a new wallet could be "
"created and copied onto a removable flash memory device. Important passwords "
"could be transferred there, so you have them available in other locations."
msgstr ""
"Kõiki sahtleid ja kirjeid saab lohistada vastavalt muusse laekasse või "
"sahtlisse. See võimaldab kasutajal mugavalt seada kokku laeka, mida siis "
"näiteks uude keskkonda üle kanda. Näiteks võib loodud uue laeka kopeerida "
"mälupulgale ja kanda nii üle olulisemad paroolid, et neid ka mujal viibides "
"edukalt kasutada."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid "Import and Export"
msgstr "Import ja eksport"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to transfer your secrets to another device or computer use the "
"actions in the <guimenu>File</guimenu> menu. With <guimenuitem>Export as "
"encrypted</guimenuitem> wallets can be exported into an encrypted archive "
"file. Importing this archive file with <guimenuitem>Import encrypted</"
"guimenuitem> you have to provide the master password of the wallet."
msgstr ""
"Kui soovid oma saladused üle kanda mõnda teise seadmesse või arvutisse, "
"kasuta menüüs <guimenu>Fail</guimenu> leiduvaid käske. Käsuga "
"<guimenuitem>Ekspordi krüptitult</guimenuitem> saab turvalaekaid eksportida "
"krüptitud arhiivifaili. Arhiivifaili importimisel käsuga "
"<guimenuitem>Impordi krüptiltult</guimenuitem> tuleb anda turvalaeka "
"ülemparool."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively a <filename class=\"extension\">.xml</filename> file can be "
"used for transferring a wallet. Keep in mind that all secrets are stored as "
"plain text in this file."
msgstr ""
"Samuti saab turvalaegast üle kanda <filename class=\"extension\">.xml</"
"filename>-failina. Pane aga tähele, et selles failis on kõik saladused "
"salvestatud lihttekstina."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding Entries Manually"
msgstr "Kirjete lisamine käsitsi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the context menu with the &RMB; click on <guilabel>Maps</guilabel> or "
"<guilabel>Passwords</guilabel> in the <guilabel>Folder</guilabel> tree view. "
"Select <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>New Folder</"
"guimenuitem> and choose a name for the new entry."
msgstr ""
"Ava kontekstimenüü, klõpsates <guilabel>sahtlite</guilabel> puuvaates "
"&HPNga; sõnadele <guilabel>Nimetabelid</guilabel> või <guilabel>Paroolid</"
"guilabel>. Vali <guimenuitem>Uus</guimenuitem> või <guimenuitem>Uus sahtel</"
"guimenuitem> ja määra uue kirje nimi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the folder contents pane select <guilabel>New Folder</guilabel> from the "
"context menu of <quote>Form Data</quote> or <quote>Passwords</quote>. For "
"passwords click the <guilabel>Show Contents</guilabel> button, enter the new "
"password. For Maps you have to add a <guilabel>Key</guilabel> and a "
"<guilabel>Value</guilabel>. Click the <guilabel>Save</guilabel> button to "
"store the new entries in the encrypted wallet file."
msgstr ""
"Vali sahtli sisu paneelis <quote>vormi andmete</quote> või <quote>paroolide</"
"quote> kontekstimenüüst <guilabel>Uus sahtel</guilabel>. Paroolide puhul "
"klõpsa <guilabel>Näita sisu</guilabel> ja sisesta uus parool. Nimetabelite "
"puhul tuleb lisada <guilabel>võti</guilabel> ja <guilabel>väärtus</"
"guilabel>. Klõpsa nupule <guilabel>Salvesta</guilabel>, millega uued kirjed "
"salvestatakse krüptitud turvalaekafaili."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Applications tab</title>"
msgstr "<title>Rakenduste kaart</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Applications tab</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Rakenduste kaart</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Applications tab</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Rakenduste kaart</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Applications tab</para>"
msgstr "<para>Rakenduste kaart</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first list shows all applications currently connected to the selected "
"wallet. Use the button at the right side of each entry to disconnect the "
"application."
msgstr ""
"Esimeses loendis näeb kõiki rakendusi, mis on praegu ühendatud valitud "
"turvalaekaga. Paremal asuva nupuga saab rakenduse ühenduse katkestada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the second list all applications are displayed which are authorized to "
"access the wallet. Use the button right of each entry in the list to revoke "
"the access."
msgstr ""
"Teises loendis on näidatud kõik rakendused, millel on õigus turvalaegast "
"kasutada. Paremal asuva nupuga saab selle õiguse tühistada."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &kwallet5;"
msgstr "&kwallet5;i seadistamine"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:409
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wallet Preferences"
msgstr "Turvalaeka valikud"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwallet5; contains a small configuration panel with several options that "
"allow you to tune &kwallet5; to your personal preferences. The default "
"settings for &kwallet5; are sufficient for most users."
msgstr ""
"&kwallet5; sisaldab väikest seadistuspaneeli mitme valikuga, mis lubavad "
"häälestada &kwallet5;i just vastavalt sinu vajadustele. Enamasti peaks küll "
"väga hästi sobima ka &kwallet5;i vaikeseadistused."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check the box to enable or disable the &kde; wallet subsystem entirely. If "
"this box is unchecked, then &kwallet5; is entirely disabled and none of the "
"other options here have any effect, nor will &kwallet5; record any "
"information, or offer to fill in forms for you."
msgstr ""
"Kastikest märkides saab &kde; turvalaegaste süsteemi kas lubada või üldse "
"keelata. Kui kastike on märkimata, ei ole &kwallet5;i kasutamine lubatud ja "
"seepärast ei ole ka ühelgi muul valikul mingit mõtet, samuti ei salvesta "
"&kwallet5; mingit infot ega täida sinu eest näiteks veebivorme."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close Wallet"
msgstr "Turvalaeka sulgemine"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close when unused for:"
msgstr "Suletakse, kui ei ole kasutatud:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Close the current wallet after a period of inactivity. If you check this "
"option, set the period in the box, default is 10 minutes. When a wallet is "
"closed, the password is needed to access it again."
msgstr ""
"Aktiivne laegas suletakse pärast teatud mitteaktiivsuse perioodi. Selle "
"valimisel saab aja määrata kastis, vaikimisi on selleks 10 minutit. Kui "
"laegas suletakse, tuleb selle kasutamiseks anda uuesti parool."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close when screensaver starts"
msgstr "Suletakse ekraanisäästja käivitumisel"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Close the wallet as soon as the screen saver starts. When a wallet is "
"closed, the password is needed to access it again."
msgstr ""
"Laegas suletakse kohe ekraanisäästja käivitumisel. Kui laegas suletakse, "
"tuleb selle kasutamiseks anda uuesti parool."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close when last application stops using it"
msgstr "Suletakse, kui enam ükski rakendus seda ei kasuta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Close the wallet as soon as applications that use it have stopped. Note that "
"your wallets will only be closed when all the applications that use it have "
"stopped. When a wallet is closed, the password is needed to access it again."
msgstr ""
"Laegas suletakse pärast seda, kui seda kasutanud rakendused on suletud. Pane "
"tähele, et laegas suletakse alles pärast seda, kui kõik seda kasutanud "
"rakendused on suletud. Kui laegas suletakse, tuleb selle kasutamiseks anda "
"uuesti parool."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic Wallet Selection"
msgstr "Turvalaeka automaatne valik"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:453
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select wallet to use as default:"
msgstr "Vaikimisi kasutatav turvalaegas:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select which wallet you want to use as default wallet. Please keep in mind "
"that only the wallet named <guilabel>kdewallet</guilabel> will be opened "
"automatically at login, if this wallet and your login password are identical."
msgstr ""
"Siin saab valida, millist laegast kasutada vaikimisi turvalaekana. Arvesta "
"aga kindlasti, et ainult laegas nimega <guilabel>kdewallet</guilabel> "
"avatakse sisselogimisel automaatselt, kui selle laeka ja sinu sisselogimise "
"parool kattuvad."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:464
#, no-c-format
msgid "Different wallet for local passwords:"
msgstr "Erinev turvalaegas kohalikele paroolidele:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:466
#, no-c-format
msgid "If checked, choose a different wallet for local passwords."
msgstr "Märkimise korral saab valida erinev turvalaeka kohalikele paroolidele."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wallet Manager"
msgstr "Turvalaeka haldur"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show manager in system tray"
msgstr "Haldurit näidatakse süsteemisalves"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable the wallet manager to have its icon in the system tray."
msgstr "Märkimisel näidatakse laekahalduri ikooni süsteemisalves."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:481
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide System tray icon when last wallet closes"
msgstr "Viimase turvalaeka sulgemisel peidetakse süsteemisalve ikoon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:484
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When there is no wallet in use anymore, remove the wallet icon from the "
"system tray."
msgstr ""
"Kui ühtegi laegast enam ei kasutata, eemaldatakse laekaikoon süsteemisalvest."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally, there is a button labeled <guibutton>Launch Wallet Manager</"
"guibutton>, which does precisely that."
msgstr ""
"Siin on ka nupp <guibutton>Käivita turvalaeka haldur</guibutton>, mis just "
"seda teebki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid "This button is only visible if &kwalletmanager5; is not running"
msgstr "Seda nuppu näeb ainult siis, kui turvalaeka haldur ei tööta."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Access Control</title>"
msgstr "<title>Kasutamise kontroll</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:498
#, no-c-format
msgid "There is only one option on this page:"
msgstr "Sellel kaardil on ainult üks valik:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:502
#, no-c-format
msgid "Prompt when an application accesses a wallet"
msgstr "Küsitakse, kui rakendus püüab kasutada turvalaegast"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid "Signal you when an application gains access to a wallet."
msgstr "Kui rakendus püüab kasutada turvalaegast, antakse sellest teada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next there is a tree style view of the access controls for your wallets."
msgstr "Selle järel asub puukujuline laegaste kasutamise kontrolli vaade."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Access Control</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Kasutamise kontroll</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Access Control</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Kasutamise kontroll</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click with the &LMB; on the <guiicon>&gt;</guiicon> symbol beside a wallet "
"name to expand the tree. You will see the name of each application that has "
"asked for access to the wallet, and the policy you set for it. You cannot "
"edit policies here, or add them, but it is possible to delete an entry by "
"&RMB; clicking on it and choosing <guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem> from the "
"context menu that appears, or by simply selecting it and pressing the "
"<keysym>Del</keysym> key."
msgstr ""
"Klõps &HVNga; laeka nime ees seisval <guiicon>&gt;</guiicon>-märgil avab "
"puu. Siin on näha iga rakendus, mis on laegast kasutanud, ning reegel, mida "
"oled sellisele kasutamisele määranud. Neid reegleid ei saa siin muuta ega "
"lisada, küll saab kirje kustutada, klõpsates sellel &HPNga; ja valides käsu "
"<guimenuitem>Kustuta</guimenuitem> või lihtsalt kirjet valides ja klahvi "
"<keycap>Del</keycap> vajutades."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:531
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An application that has been allowed access to a wallet is granted access to "
"all passwords stored inside."
msgstr ""
"Rakendus, millele on lubatud ligipääs turvalaekale, saab ligipääsu kõigile "
"sellesse salvestatud paroolidele."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you erroneously configured an application not to use the &kwallet5; "
"delete the policy for this application here."
msgstr ""
"Kui oled ekslikult määranud, et rakendus ei kasuta turvalaeka haldurit "
"&kwallet5;, saab siin selle rakenduse reegli kustutada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the next start of this application you can define a new policy for access "
"to the wallet."
msgstr ""
"Selle rakenduse järgmisel käivitamisel saab kindlaks määrata turvalaeka "
"kasutamise uue reegli."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Access request to open a wallet</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Turvalaeka avamise õiguse päring</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Access request to open a wallet</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Turvalaeka avamise õiguse päring</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:549
#, no-c-format
msgid "An application requesting access to a wallet"
msgstr "Rakendus soovib kasutada turvalaegast"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:558
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced Features"
msgstr "Muud võimalused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:560
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Wallets can be dragged from the &kwalletmanager5; window. This allows you to "
"drag the wallet to a file browser window, where you can choose to copy, "
"move, or link the wallet, as desired."
msgstr ""
"Turvalaekaid on võimalik turvalaeka halduri aknast lohistada näiteks "
"faililehitseja aknasse, kus saab selle vajalikku kohta kopeerida, liigutada "
"või linkida."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:564
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You might use this to save a wallet to portable media, such as a USB "
"keychain, so that you can take your passwords with you to work or on a "
"vacation, and still have easy access to important sites."
msgstr ""
"Seda võimalust saab kasutada turvalaeka salvestamiseks kaasaskantavale "
"andmekandjale, näiteks USB mälupulgale, mis lubab paroolid tööle või "
"puhkusereisile kaasa võtta ja nii hõlpsasti olulistele kohtadele ligi "
"pääseda."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid "Credits and License"
msgstr "Autorid ja litsents"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:573
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kwallet5; &copy; 2003 &George.Staikos;"
msgstr "&kwallet5; &copy; 2003: &George.Staikos;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:574
#, no-c-format
msgid "Documentation &copy; &Lauri.Watts; and &George.Staikos;"
msgstr "Dokumentatsioon &copy;: &Lauri.Watts; ja &George.Staikos;"

